pan class=\"token punctuation\">%</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nis_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>john<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># ** (KeyError) key :gender not found</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">%</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">gender:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"male\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># holds the name of the struct</span>\njohn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__struct__</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"accessing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#accessing\" aria-label=\"accessing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Accessing</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elixir\"><pre class=\"language-elixir\"><code class=\"language-elixir\">user <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">%</span>User<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">name:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Tony Stark\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">age:</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nuser<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name\nuser<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>age</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"updating\" style=\"position:rel